<div class="title">Perfect For Drunkards and Those Alike</div>
<div class="substance">Milk Thistle & Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=%3A%29&Exact=1">:)</a></div>


